  Locus:
    Page: 102
    Verse: 18
Tags:
  - Desire
---
The man who seeks one, and but one thing in life may hope to achieve it,
but he who seeks all things, wherever he goes, only reaps from the hopes
which he sows, a harvest of barren regrets.
